ht:bold;\"><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;\"><span style=\"font-family:맑은 고딕;\">『</span></span></span><span style=\"font-weight:bold;\"><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;\"><span style=\"font-family:맑은 고딕;\">미당 서정주 전집</span></span></span><span style=\"letter-spacing:0pt;font-weight:bold;\"><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;\"><span style=\"font-family:맑은 고딕;\">』</span></span></span><span style=\"letter-spacing:0pt;font-weight:bold;\"><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;\"><span style=\"font-family:맑은 고딕;\">(</span></span></span><span style=\"font-weight:bold;\"><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;\"><span style=\"font-family:맑은 고딕;\">전</span></span></span><span style=\"letter-spacing:0pt;font-weight:bold;\"><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;\"><span style=\"font-family:맑은 고딕;\">20</span></span></span><span style=\"font-weight:bold;\"><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;\"><span style=\"font-family:맑은 고딕;\">권</span></span></span><span style=\"letter-spacing:0pt;font-weight:bold;\"><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;\"><span style=\"font-family:맑은 고딕;\">,</span></span></span></p>\n<p style=\"margin-left:10.0pt;text-indent:-10.0pt;text-autospace:none;\"><span style=\"font-weight:bold;\"><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;\"><span style=\"font-family:맑은 고딕;\">은행나무</span></span></span><span style=\"letter-spacing:0pt;font-weight:bold;\"><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;\"><span style=\"font-family:맑은 고딕;\">, 2017)</span></span></span><span style=\"font-weight:bold;\"><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;\"><span style=\"font-family:맑은 고딕;\">에서 인용함을 원칙으로 함</span></span></span></p>\n<p style=\"margin-left:10.0pt;text-indent:-10.0pt;text-autospace:none;\"><span style=\"letter-spacing:0pt;\"><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;\"><span style=\"font-family:맑은 고딕;\">• </span></span></span><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;\"><span style=\"font-family:맑은 고딕;\">미발표 신규 논문이 수상작으로 결정될 경우</span></span><span style=\"letter-spacing:0pt;\"><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;\"><span style=\"font-family:맑은 고딕;\">, </span></span></span><s